012200
012300 ROT-DELETE-FILE.
012400
012500     DISPLAY 'ROT-DELETE-FILE'.
012600
012700     ADD 01 TO WSS-REG-LIDOS.

           DISPLAY ' FS-EMP-ID  = ' FS-EMP-ID.

012900     DELETE EMPFILE
013100              INVALID KEY PERFORM VSAM-CODE-DISPLAY
013200          NOT INVALID KEY PERFORM ROT-DISPLAY
